hopobject.body: Do you like it here? dulcolax bisacodyl usp 5 mg It’s not something that many consider, but how do the astronauts stationed aboard the International Space Station stay clean? With no gravity and little privacy, it is a more complicated matter than simply hopping into the shower. ISS astronaut Karen Nyberg, the only female astronaut currently living aboard the International Space Station, recorded a three-minute video in space demonstrating how she washes her hair– with no gravity and no running water.
